snippet.title: Super mario 64 x Ocarina of Time Release Trailer (commentated)
snippet.description:
The second commentated reupload of an old release that was taken down earlier!
For more fangames, subscribe!: https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1
Demos, funding: https://www.patreon.com/Kazestuff
I do livestreams!: https://www.twitch.tv/kazesm64


Note: Enable 8MB ram in the emulators settings or it will only give you a black screen.
Download:
https://mega.nz/#!KOhgAYTa!zVs_eT0kHJ7v4DGcEl-88IFVXao3YssUQSzu4Temo98
